OL,3,CShoplifting - Who's Paying the Price?
OL,5,FIt's been a turbulent few years for
OL,6,Fthe retail industry, but businesses
OL,7,Fwho have weathered the storms now face
OL,8,Fanother threat ` shoplifters. Police-
OL,9,Freported shoplifting offences in
OL,10,FEngland and Wales reached their
OL,11,Fhighest ever levels this year, and
OL,12,Fretailers say many more incidents go
OL,13,Funreported.
