OL,3,CShoplifting - Who's Paying the Price?
OL,5,FOne business feeling the strain is
OL,6,FBrowns, a family-owned department
OL,7,Fstore that has served customers since
OL,8,F1890. At its Beverley branch in East
OL,9,FYorkshire, Manager Sarah Walker says
OL,10,Fthey are facing increasingly brazen
OL,11,Fand organised thefts. Their CCTV has
OL,12,Fcaptured groups of men repeatedly
OL,13,Ftargeting high-end perfumes and
OL,14,Fcosmetics.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
