OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F311A1763669751
OL,3,CShoplifting - Who's Paying the Price?
OL,5,F"We have been hit a couple of times
OL,6,Fnow by people coming in and literally
OL,7,Fgoing for it. Doesn't matter who or
OL,8,Fwhat's in the way ` they will just get
OL,9,Fwhat they want. It's always high end
OL,10,Fproducts. I do believe that they come
OL,11,Fin with a shopping list."
OL,13,F` Sarah Walker, Browns Department Store
OL,15,FThe thefts have left employees fearing
OL,16,Ffor their safety, and Browns has now
OL,17,Fintroduced panic alarms in an effort
OL,18,Fto protect its staff.
