OL,3,CShoplifting - Who's Paying the Price?
OL,5,F"We've apprehended people and we've
OL,6,Fhad police attend. There have been
OL,7,Ftimes where they haven't attended.
OL,8,FThere have been times where we've sent
OL,9,Fin CCTV images. Half the time I don't
OL,10,Feven bother. The only way this is
OL,11,Fgonna alleviate is if more police are
OL,12,Frecruited, if they're given a bigger
OL,13,Fbudget, if they're given the
OL,14,Fresources. We're asking for help ` we
OL,15,Fdo feel abandoned."
OL,17,F` Kaual, Torridon Convenience
