OL,5,F"This is an area that's gone unchecked
OL,6,Ffor some time. We will deal with any
OL,7,Fof the crimes that are reported and
OL,8,Fit's now for us to get that
OL,9,Finformation out to the public so they
OL,10,Fcan see exactly what we're doing."
OL,12,F` Commander Andy Featherstone,
OL,13,FMetropolitan Police
OL,15,FMany will now be hoping that a renewed
OL,16,Ffocus on tackling the issue, continues
OL,17,Fto get results.
