OL,5,FIn the meantime, Paul Brand asks what
OL,6,Fcan be done to ensure that the true
OL,7,Fcost of shoplifting doesn't affect the
OL,8,Fvery people working hardest to keep
OL,9,Ftheir communities running.
OL,11,FShoplifting - Who's Paying the Price?
OL,12,Fis on ITV1 on Thursday 20th November
OL,13,Fat 7:30pm.
